          "character": "龙王",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江河湖海透九霄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙王",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "清波摆动浪滔滔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，四海龙王是也。只因紫微星君，身临水府有难，须得吾神前去搭救。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凌霄宝殿居水府"
